.IP fixedbold 4
.IX Item "fixedbold"
[1.00] Bold version of the fixed-width font.  Defaults to \f(CW\*(C`CB\*(C'\fR.  Only matters
for \fBtroff\fR output.
.IP fixeditalic 4
.IX Item "fixeditalic"
[1.00] Italic version of the fixed-width font (something of a misnomer, since
