.Sp
Also see the \f(CW\*(C`quotes\*(C'\fR option, which can be used to set both quotes at once.
If both \f(CW\*(C`quotes\*(C'\fR and one of the other options is set, \f(CW\*(C`lquote\*(C'\fR or \f(CW\*(C`rquote\*(C'\fR
